 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x : A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}Bx satisfying \mathsf {ind}_{A,a}\,b\,a = b.

Then we compute \mathsf {ind}_{A,a}\,b\,a \equiv  
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen \chi _a^{-1}\cdot \chi _a\right \rparen \mathclose {}
_* b  = \mathsf {refl}_*b = b.

